body_html: @ezyang @yf225 Wait, I cannot reproduce it on two of my machines. So I guess that must be something else wrong there. For your information, the CMake versions are 3.8.2 and 3.10.2, and both machines use Ninja 1.8.2. And the MSVC version is a bit newer than the CI one, which is 19.11.25547. The git on two machines share the same version 2.15.1.windows.2.
